---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Hypersleep Technology"
  description="Weyland-Yutani's hypersleep technology enables complete cessation of biological processes with full reversibility. Patented 2030, enabling interstellar travel spanning decades or centuries."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden scanlines border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 py-24">
        <div class="max-w-5xl">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
            <a href="/technology" class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:text-[#FFC600] transition-colors">TECHNOLOGY</a>
            <span class="text-gray-700">/</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">HYPERSLEEP</span>
          </div>

          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black text-white mb-6 leading-[0.9] uppercase">
            HYPERSLEEP<br/><span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">TECHNOLOGY</span>
          </h1>

          <div class="h-1 w-48 bg-[#FFC600] mb-8"></div>

          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl uppercase tracking-wide font-mono leading-relaxed">
            COMPLETE CESSATION OF ALL BIOLOGICAL PROCESSES WITH FULL REVERSIBILITY. THE ENABLING TECHNOLOGY FOR INTERSTELLAR HUMAN TRANSIT.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Metrics -->
    <section class="relative py-16 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-2">2028</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-[0.15em]">CAPABILITY DISCOVERED</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-2">2030</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-[0.15em]">CHAMBER PATENTED</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-2">99.98%</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-[0.15em]">REVIVAL SUCCESS</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-2">2M+</div>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-[0.15em]">CYCLES COMPLETED</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Technical Overview -->
    <section class="relative py-32 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 max-w-7xl">
          <div>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">TECHNICAL OVERVIEW</div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-8 uppercase">THE SCIENCE OF STASIS</h2>

            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              IN 2028, WEYLAND CORPORATION BIOMEDICAL RESEARCHERS ACHIEVED WHAT HAD PREVIOUSLY BEEN CONSIDERED BIOLOGICALLY IMPOSSIBLE: THE COMPLETE AND REVERSIBLE CESSATION OF ALL LIFE PROCESSES IN A HUMAN SUBJECT. THE DISCOVERY EMERGED FROM ADVANCED CRYOBIOLOGY RESEARCH AND REPRESENTED A FUNDAMENTAL BREAKTHROUGH IN OUR UNDERSTANDING OF CELLULAR PRESERVATION.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              THE HYPERSLEEP PROCESS INDUCES A STATE OF TOTAL METABOLIC SUSPENSION. CELLULAR ACTIVITY CEASES ENTIRELY. NEURAL FUNCTION HALTS. THE SUBJECT ENTERS A STATE INDISTINGUISHABLE FROM DEATH BY ALL CONVENTIONAL METRICS, YET REMAINS FULLY VIABLE FOR REVIVAL AT ANY POINT.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              THE PROPRIETARY STASIS INDUCTION SEQUENCE INVOLVES A PRECISELY CONTROLLED COMBINATION OF ATMOSPHERIC MODIFICATION WITHIN THE SEALED CHAMBER, CORE TEMPERATURE REDUCTION, AND CELLULAR STABILIZATION COMPOUNDS DELIVERED TRANSDERMALLY. THE ENTIRE PROCESS FROM CONSCIOUSNESS TO FULL STASIS TAKES APPROXIMATELY 12 MINUTES.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed">
              REVIVAL IS INITIATED BY THE CHAMBER'S ONBOARD SYSTEMS AND FOLLOWS A STAGED REWARMING AND METABOLIC REACTIVATION PROTOCOL LASTING 30 TO 45 MINUTES. SUBJECTS REPORT NO SUBJECTIVE AWARENESS OF ELAPSED TIME, REGARDLESS OF STASIS DURATION.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="terminal">
              <div class="terminal-content">
                <div class="mb-4">
                  <span class="text-gray-500">// HYPERSLEEP SYSTEM PARAMETERS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-xs">
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> INDUCTION TIME: <span class="text-white">~12 MINUTES</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> REVIVAL TIME: <span class="text-white">30-45 MINUTES</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> METABOLIC STATE: <span class="text-white">COMPLETE SUSPENSION</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> NEURAL ACTIVITY: <span class="text-white">ZERO (FULL CESSATION)</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> CORE TEMP (STASIS): <span class="text-white">-4C (STABILIZED)</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> MAX DURATION: <span class="text-white">UNLIMITED (THEORETICAL)</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> REVIVAL SUCCESS: <span class="text-white">99.98%</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> AGING DURING STASIS: <span class="text-white">ZERO</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> CONSCIOUSNESS DURING: <span class="text-white">NONE</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> MONITORING: <span class="text-white">CONTINUOUS BIOMETRIC</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> POWER MODE: <span class="text-white">LOW-DRAW / SHIP GRID</span></div>
                  <div><span class="text-gray-500">&gt;</span> EMERGENCY WAKE: <span class="text-white">AVAILABLE AT ALL TIMES</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="corp-card p-6">
              <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-3">SAFETY RECORD</div>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
                WITH OVER 2 MILLION COMPLETED HYPERSLEEP CYCLES AND A 99.98% REVIVAL SUCCESS RATE, WEYLAND-YUTANI HYPERSLEEP TECHNOLOGY HAS BEEN CERTIFIED AS SAFE FOR ALL HUMAN SUBJECTS BETWEEN THE AGES OF 4 AND 85. ADVERSE EVENTS ARE LIMITED TO TRANSIENT DISORIENTATION IN APPROXIMATELY 3% OF REVIVAL CASES.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Applications -->
    <section class="relative py-32 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-y-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
          <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">APPLICATIONS</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase">DEPLOYMENT SCENARIOS</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-6xl">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">INTERSTELLAR TRANSIT</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              THE PRIMARY APPLICATION OF HYPERSLEEP TECHNOLOGY. CREW AND PASSENGERS ENTER STASIS FOR THE DURATION OF FTL TRANSIT, ELIMINATING THE NEED FOR LIFE SUPPORT PROVISIONS AND ENSURING ARRIVAL WITHOUT PHYSICAL OR PSYCHOLOGICAL EFFECTS OF LONG-DURATION SPACEFLIGHT.
            </p>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase">STANDARD ON ALL FTL-EQUIPPED VESSELS</div>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">COLONY TRANSPORT</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              MASS COLONIAL TRANSPORT UTILIZES HIGH-DENSITY HYPERSLEEP CONFIGURATIONS TO MOVE THOUSANDS OF SETTLERS PER VOYAGE. COLONISTS ENTER STASIS AT THE DEPARTURE PORT AND AWAKE AT THEIR DESTINATION, REGARDLESS OF TRANSIT DURATION.
            </p>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase">BULK CHAMBER ARRAYS, 500-5000 CAPACITY</div>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">MEDICAL PRESERVATION</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              PATIENTS WITH CONDITIONS REQUIRING TREATMENT FACILITIES NOT AVAILABLE AT THEIR CURRENT LOCATION CAN ENTER HYPERSLEEP FOR TRANSPORT. STASIS HALTS DISEASE PROGRESSION ENTIRELY, ENABLING SAFE TRANSIT TO SPECIALIZED MEDICAL CENTERS.
            </p>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase">MEDICAL-GRADE CHAMBERS WITH ENHANCED MONITORING</div>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">EMERGENCY SURVIVAL</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              THE LUXURY SURVIVAL POD (PATENTED 2057) COMBINES HYPERSLEEP CAPABILITY WITH A SELF-CONTAINED LIFE SUPPORT AND EMERGENCY BEACON SYSTEM. DESIGNED FOR 50-YEAR AUTONOMOUS OPERATION, ENABLING SURVIVAL IN THE EVENT OF VESSEL CATASTROPHE.
            </p>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase">50-YEAR AUTONOMOUS LIFESPAN / EMERGENCY BEACON</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Integration with Ship Systems -->
    <section class="relative py-32 bg-black">
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
          <div>
            <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">VESSEL INTEGRATION</div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase">SHIPBOARD SYSTEMS</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              HYPERSLEEP CHAMBERS ARE FULLY INTEGRATED WITH VESSEL LIFE SUPPORT, NAVIGATION, AND AI MANAGEMENT SYSTEMS. THE MUTHUR SHIPBOARD AI MONITORS ALL CHAMBER FUNCTIONS DURING TRANSIT AND MANAGES THE WAKE CYCLE ACCORDING TO MISSION PARAMETERS.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              EMERGENCY WAKE PROTOCOLS CAN BE TRIGGERED BY THE AI, THE SHIP'S SYNTHETIC CREW MEMBER, OR AUTOMATED SAFETY SYSTEMS IN RESPONSE TO VESSEL EMERGENCIES. CHAMBER ARRAYS ARE LOCATED IN DEDICATED STASIS DECKS WITH INDEPENDENT ENVIRONMENTAL CONTROL AND STRUCTURAL HARDENING.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed">
              ALL CHAMBERS INCORPORATE REDUNDANT POWER SUPPLIES AND BACKUP LIFE SUPPORT. IN THE EVENT OF TOTAL VESSEL POWER LOSS, CHAMBERS AUTOMATICALLY TRANSITION TO INTERNAL BATTERY MODE WITH A MINIMUM 72-HOUR CAPACITY TO ALLOW FOR CONTROLLED EMERGENCY REVIVAL.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="corp-card p-6">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-4 uppercase">SAFETY PROTOCOLS</h3>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">01</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">CONTINUOUS BIOMETRIC MONITORING (HEARTBEAT, NEURAL, CELLULAR)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">02</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">TRIPLE-REDUNDANT ENVIRONMENTAL CONTROL</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">03</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">BACKUP POWER (72-HOUR MINIMUM)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">04</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">EMERGENCY WAKE CAPABILITY (AUTOMATED AND MANUAL)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">05</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">STRUCTURAL HARDENING AGAINST IMPACT AND DECOMPRESSION</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black text-xs">06</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">MUTHUR AI CONTINUOUS OVERSIGHT AND REPORTING</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="corp-card p-6">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-4 uppercase">LUXURY SURVIVAL POD</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase leading-relaxed mb-3">
                PATENTED 2057. SELF-CONTAINED HYPERSLEEP SYSTEM WITH INDEPENDENT POWER, LIFE SUPPORT, AND EMERGENCY LOCATOR BEACON. DESIGNED FOR EXECUTIVE PROTECTION AND EMERGENCY EVACUATION SCENARIOS.
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs">&gt;</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">AUTONOMOUS LIFESPAN: 50 YEARS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs">&gt;</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">DISTRESS BEACON RANGE: 100+ LIGHT-YEARS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs">&gt;</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">MICRO-THRUSTER NAVIGATION CAPABILITY</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="relative py-20 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-2 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase">EXPLORE HYPERSLEEP PRODUCTS</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          VIEW OUR COMPLETE LINE OF HYPERSLEEP CHAMBERS, FROM STANDARD CREW CONFIGURATIONS TO LUXURY EXECUTIVE PODS AND MILITARY-GRADE UNITS.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/products/hypersleep-chambers" class="btn-primary">VIEW PRODUCTS</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary">CONTACT SALES</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
